snippet.title: Amber Heard Just Comes Out Of The Closet As 'LESBIAN' After These Pic!!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard may have a new lady in her life. The Aquaman star, 33, was seen getting cozy with filmmaker Bianca Butti during a trip to Palm Springs on Sunday. While waiting at a valet stand, Heard and Butti were spotted locking lips before hopping into a red vintage Mustang together.
